{"tid":1553770,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"(和理非活動) 見到廣告板滑倒了，請通知廣告商叫黨鐵回水","createTime":"2019-09-08T17:05:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T02:43:40.000Z","uid":14918,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"85544b955aca0a44eb03724ef8099f3d221071c4","tid":1553770,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T17:05:11.000Z","msg":"事緣出面有個po係講今日快閃灣仔站<br />\n<br />\n都見到好多廣告板如下圖都滑倒到<br />\n有記性既巴打，請記住係咩廣告商<br />\n係FB通知番間公司「你個廣告無左呀，快啲叫MTR回水啦」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pQM0P9x.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpQM0P9x.png&h=d4c56691&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.jcdecaux.com.hk/documents/mtr/MTR-PosterAd_FeatureAd-2013-201300509_r.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.jcdecaux.com.hk%2Fdocuments%2Fmtr%2FMTR-PosterAd_FeatureAd-2013-201300509_r.pdf&d=h%2B0F1AfFk4MBaO73S6qK%2BpB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=4f36a0f1\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.jcdecaux.com.hk/documents/mtr/MTR-PosterAd_FeatureAd-2013-201300509_r.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n呢個係2013年廣告收費表，呢啲咁既12sheets都要每星期十幾萬架<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nP.S. 最近廣告商都唔落ads比黨鐵了<br />\n發唔發覺多左好多機場快綫、落馬洲/高鐵廣告<br />\n啲poster位賣唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家搵殘體字廣告，叫人去大陸整試管嬰兒都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5e1aec91067a726c4ed1b45a90b8d249d2ecb23","tid":1553770,"uid":251769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T17:06:27.000Z","msg":"「緊急」十八區中學人鏈聽朝要人 入嚟睇下有冇你舊校<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1553681\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1553681</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"34766e6629ad53205f84f15fae6a954fd80f2b42","tid":1553770,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"